quota-applet (1.2.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * notified is stored as variable, no need for file in temp
  * Info string
  * Fixes - use popen so exit_code != 0 doesnt trigger exception
  * use XDG_CACHE_HOME for temporary files
  * Show notifications when disk space will be excceeded soon
  * Fixed string for notification
  * Check if quota is set for user
  * Readme: added build dependencies
  * debian: added missing Source
  * Use debuild for package building
  * Updated debian package


