quota-applet (1.1.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Fixed another deprecated issues
  * install sigint handler so no exception is thrown on ctrl+c
  * Green color for disk usage under the threshold
  * check_interval is configurable from cli parameter
  * Check_interval reduced to 15s
  * Added dependency
  * Simplified getting homedir and username
  * Fixed deprecated issues
  * Open baobab to examine disk usage
  * Raise exception if quota parsing failed instead of silent exit.

